'''新澤西理工學院'''（'''New Jersey Institute of Technology'''，縮寫：'''NJIT'''）是位於美國[[新澤西州|新澤西州]][[紐華克_(新澤西州)|紐華克]]的一所[[公立大學|公立]][[研究型大學|研究型大學]]，創立於1881年。<ref>{{cite web |title=State of New Jersey Commission on Higher Education: NJ College & University Directory by Sector |publisher=State of New Jersey |url=http://www.state.nj.us/highereducation/colleges/schools_sector.htm#pru |accessdate=October 2, 2011 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924130500/http://www.state.nj.us/highereducation/colleges/schools_sector.htm#pru |dead-url=no }}</ref> 該學院坐落於[[紐約大都會區|紐約大都會區]]內，距離紐華克市中心很近，距離紐約市也只有{{convert|14.5|km}}，交通便捷。<ref>{{cite news|title=Warren Street stop on Newark Subway line to get $40K makeover with help of NJIT students|url=http://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/03/warren_street_stop_on_newark_s.html|last=Heyboer|first=Kelly|accessdate=December 12, 2014|newspaper=The Star-Ledger|date=March 4, 2011|archive-date=2018-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181120084834/https://www.nj.com/news/index.ssf/2011/03/warren_street_stop_on_newark_s.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==历史==

[[File:Eberhardt_Hall_NJIT_jeh.JPG|thumb]]
1881年纽瓦克技术学校（Newark Technical School）设立，此即新泽西理工学院的前身，该学校在1884年开课。艾伦·R·卡利莫尔（Allan R. Cullimore）在1920年至1949年担任其校长，任期内的1930年将其改为纽瓦克工程学院（Newark College of Engineering）<ref>{{cite web |title=History of the Newark Technical School and the Newark College of Engineering. |author=Allan R. Cullimore |year=1955 |publisher=unpublished manuscript in the Van Houten Library at NJIT, Newark, NJ. |url=http://archives.njit.edu/vhlib/hist-cullimore/njit-hist-cullimore.pdf |accessdate=June 15, 2006 |archive-date=2013-10-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004215249/http://archives.njit.edu/vhlib/hist-cullimore/njit-hist-cullimore.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

1973年新泽西建筑学校（New Jersey School of Architecture）并入该校，1975年纽瓦克工程学院改现名，以示其课程涵盖各类理工学科。1979年盖起第一座学生公寓“Redwood Hall”。

